{"type":null,"faqId":33924,"title":"什么是智能语音","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.39375in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>长按荣耀智灵键（默认设置下），听到提示音“滴”后，可以说出要做的事情，让手机替您完成。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>例如：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>“打电话给张三”，可拨打张三的手机号。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>“帮我设一个早晨六点半的闹钟”，可设置闹钟。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>“提醒我4月20号买火车票”，可设置日历提醒。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>“帮我记一下，去超市记得买酸奶”，可创建备忘录。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>“发微信给张三”，可进入“张三”的微信对话界面。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>如要了解更多语音命令示例，说出“帮助”即可。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>提示：您还可以打开“设置-&gt;智灵”，在智灵中设置智能语音的开启方式。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":144,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"8626","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1436748763000,"seriesProductName":"PLK-AL10,PLK-CL00,PLK-TL00,PLK-TL01H,PLK-UL00","visitedTimes":64,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"智能语音","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}